<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>OTP Verfication template</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="context">
            <p>Hello{{ cardHolderName}},</p>
            <p>We received a request for Credit Card Block. Please use the followiing OTP. </p>
            <div class="info">
                <h2>One-Time Password (OTP)</h2>
                <p>OTP : {{otp}}</p>
                <p>Use this OTP to Block Your Credit Card. Please do not share this OTP with anyone for security reasons.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p style="color:#57b846; text-align:center;margin-top:100px;font-size:18px">&copy; {{company}}</p>

        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>